OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FDry with plenty of sunshine,
OL,6,Falthough it will often be hazy.
OL,7,FBecoming very warm or perhaps hot for
OL,8,Fmost places away from the coast, where
OL,9,Fcooling onshore breezes will occur.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FMainly dry with a mix of
OL,12,Fcloudier spells and clear periods,
OL,13,Falthough there is a chance of a few
OL,14,Fshowers arriving, these most likely
OL,15,Facross the Peak District.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FBright or sunny spells and
OL,18,Fisolated light showers, these most
OL,19,Flikely across the Peak District.
OL,20,FTemperatures will be noticeably lower
OL,21,Fthan previous days.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
