OL,3,GEast Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FMonday
OL,6,Fdry start then rain spreads east,
OL,7,Fbecoming heavy later. Tuesday sunshine
OL,8,Fand showers, some heavy with perhaps
OL,9,Fhail and thunder. Wednesday mainly dry
OL,10,Fand fine before rain arrives later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
